OL,3,CWoman who lost nearly #100,000 wants
OL,4,Cscam victims treated with more care
OL,6,FA Jersey woman who was scammed out of
OL,7,Fmore than #90,0000 says getting the
OL,8,Fmoney back has been "the most
OL,9,Fstressful period of my life".
OL,11,FDeirdre Bates was targeted in August
OL,12,F2023 by fraudsters over the phone who
OL,13,Fpretended to be from her bank
OL,14,Fenquiring about a large fashion
OL,15,Fpurchase.
OL,17,FAfter 16 months, she has now been able
OL,18,Fto recover the money - but said it has
OL,19,Fbeen "the most stressful period of my
OL,20,Flife".
