OL,3,CWoman who lost nearly #100,000 wants
OL,4,Cscam victims treated with more care
OL,6,FShe adds: "I did have lots of
OL,7,Fsleepless nights, lots of tears were
OL,8,Fshed.
OL,10,FDeidre also emphasised how hard it has
OL,11,Fbeen to get that money back, saying:
OL,12,F"They were making it so difficult for
OL,13,Fme ... it's been 16 months of absolute
OL,14,Ftorture.
OL,16,F"I've spent hours researching,
OL,17,Fappointments, sending emails,
OL,18,Flistening to recordings ... it was
OL,19,Frelentless."
