OL,3,CWoman who lost nearly #100,000 wants
OL,4,Cscam victims treated with more care
OL,6,FWhen someone has already lost money,
OL,7,FBarry Faudemer, CEO of Baker
OL,8,FRegulatory Services, said: "I think
OL,9,Fthe level of service that's offered to
OL,10,Fvictims of fraud and scams needs to
OL,11,Fimprove.
OL,13,F"We've seen some worrying reports from
OL,14,Fthe people we've had contact with that
OL,15,Fthe levels of service have been very
OL,16,Fpoor and there needs to be a speed of
OL,17,Fresponse.
OL,19,F"They need to get through to someone
OL,20,Fon the telephone. It's as simple as
OL,21,Fthat."
