OL,3,CWoman who lost nearly #100,000 wants
OL,4,Cscam victims treated with more care
OL,6,FHe suggests that Jersey should follow
OL,7,Fthe UK which has recently introduced a
OL,8,Flaw ensuring banks must refund up to
OL,9,F#85,000 to victims of fraud within
OL,10,Ffive days.
OL,12,FBarry explains: "I think we need to
OL,13,Ffollow suit - I can't see any good
OL,14,Freason why we should be out of step
OL,15,Fwith the UK with the legislation that
OL,16,Fthey are invoking to protect consumers.
