OL,3,CWoman who lost nearly #100,000 wants
OL,4,Cscam victims treated with more care
OL,6,F"In Jersey, we've seen a surge in
OL,7,F2024, where victims of all ages have
OL,8,Ffallen victim to push payment frauds -
OL,9,Fwhich is where fraudsters pretend to
OL,10,Fbe the security of a bank department."
OL,12,FDeirdre now hopes that sharing her
OL,13,Fexperience will prevent others from
OL,14,Ffalling victim to scams.
